ultural Society Pumpkin Contest.</li>\r\n	<li>Entrants are free to use any pumpkin seed. The Society will provide seeds to all school aged children in the upper Pontiac.</li>\r\n</ol>', 'Just For Fun', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '14-revision-9', '', '', '2012-03-29 18:46:19', '2012-03-29 18:46:19', '', 14, 'http://chapeau.phpfogapp.com/2012/03/14-revision-9/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
